**Recommendations:**

Get the [Day Dream](https://modrinth.com/mod/day-dream/) mod so you can sleep during the day to make it night!

Get the [Daylight Mobs Reborn](https://modrinth.com/mod/daylight-mobs-reborn/) mod and enable the toggle that allows hostile mobs to spawn during the day! No mobs will burn in the day and you'll have an even bigger challenge trying to survive.
